cast.overview: Will Kane, the sheriff of a small town in New Mexico, learns a notorious outlaw he put in jail has been freed, and will be arriving on the noon train. Knowing the outlaw and his gang are coming to kill him, Kane is determined to stand his ground, so he attempts to gather a posse from among the local townspeople.
cast.title: High Noon

cast.overview: A disillusioned college graduate finds himself torn between his older lover and her daughter.
cast.title: The Graduate

details.biography:
From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia

Eve McVeagh (born Eva Elizabeth McVeagh; July 15, 1919 – December 10, 1997) was an American actress of film, television, stage, and radio. Her career spanned 52 years from her first stage role through her last stage appearance. McVeagh's roles included leading and supporting parts as well as smaller character roles in which she proved a gifted character actress.
details.name: Eve McVeagh
